No. 13674. Lane, Admx., v. The Youngstown Sheet & Tube Co. Error to Circuit Court of Mahoning county. Messrs. W. S. Anderson & Son,- for plaintiff in error. Messrs. Hine, Kennedy & Manchester, for defendant in error. Judgment affirmed. Nichols, C. J., Johnson, Donahue, Wanamaker, Newman and Wilkin, JJ., concur.

Decided March 10, 1914.
